### API Gateway - Assignment Service Integration Examples

### 1. Get all assignments
GET http://localhost:3000/assignments

### 2. Get assignment by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/assignments/a82940b0-cff0-42df-b4c4-0ff66a2a30fc

### 3. Create new assignment
POST http://localhost:3000/assignments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Функція для обчислення суми масиву",
  "description": "Напишіть функцію, яка обчислює суму всіх елементів масиву.",
  "difficulty": 2,
  "deadline": "2024-12-31T23:59:59.000Z",
  "testCases": [
    {
      "input": "[1, 2, 3, 4, 5]",
      "expected": "15",
      "description": "Сума масиву [1, 2, 3, 4, 5]"
    },
    {
      "input": "[]",
      "expected": "0",
      "description": "Сума порожнього масиву"
    }
  ]
}

### 4. Update assignment
PATCH http://localhost:3000/assignments/a82940b0-cff0-42df-b4c4-0ff66a2a30fc
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Оновлена назва завдання",
  "difficulty": 4
}

### 5. Delete assignment
DELETE http://localhost:3000/assignments/a82940b0-cff0-42df-b4c4-0ff66a2a30fc

### 6. Get all submissions
GET http://localhost:3000/submissions

### 7. Get submission by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/submissions/89d47645-d28e-480c-8de7-a41b556fa93c

### 8. Get submissions by user
GET http://localhost:3000/submissions/user/user123

### 9. Get submissions by assignment
GET http://localhost:3000/submissions/assignment/a82940b0-cff0-42df-b4c4-0ff66a2a30fc

### 10. Create new submission
POST http://localhost:3000/submissions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user123",
  "assignmentId": "a82940b0-cff0-42df-b4c4-0ff66a2a30fc",
  "code": "function factorial(n) {\n  if (n === 0 || n === 1) return 1;\n  return n * factorial(n - 1);\n}"
}

### 11. Delete submission
DELETE http://localhost:3000/submissions/89d47645-d28e-480c-8de7-a41b556fa93c

